Introduction

EXO-SC, also known as EXO Se-Chan, is a sub-unit of the boy group EXO under SM Entertainment. SC stands for the members intials: Sehun and Chanyeol. The duo made their official debut on July 22, 2019 with the mini-album "What a Life".
